m ibn Ya'qub al-Juzajani</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">4th/10th</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Abu Bakr al-Ajurri</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Abu_Bakr_al-Khallal\" title=\"Abu Bakr al-Khallal\">Abu Bakr al-Khallal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Al-Hasan_ibn_Ali_al-Barbahari\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Al-Hasan ibn Ali al-Barbahari\">Al-Hasan ibn Ali al-Barbahari</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ibn_Battah\" title=\"Ibn Battah\">Ibn Battah</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ibn_Manda\" title=\"Ibn Manda\">Ibn Manda</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">5th/11th</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Abu_Saeed_Mubarak_Makhzoomi\" title=\"Abu Saeed Mubarak Makhzoomi\">Abu Saeed Mubarak Makhzoomi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Al-Qadi_Abu_Ya%27la\" title=\"Al-Qadi Abu Ya&#39;la\">Al-Qadi Abu Ya'la</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ibn_Aqil\" title=\"Ibn Aqil\">Ibn Aqil</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Khwaja_Abdullah_Ansari\" title=\"Khwaja Abdullah Ansari\">Khwaja Abdullah Ansari</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">6th/12th</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Abdul-Razzaq_Gilani\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Abdul-Razzaq Gilani\">Abdul-Razzaq Gilani</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Abdul-Qadir_Gilani\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Abdul-Qadir Gilani\">Abdul-Qadir Gilani</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Awn_ad-Din